                                            <article>
                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">I am thankful for the numerous opportunities RCHK has provided me, particularly in supporting my CAS project, which has immensely helped me to orient myself and foster my interest in a career in medicine and global health.</p>
                                                        <button class="view-more">
                                                            <span>View More</span>
                                                        </button>
