                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">RCHK’s inclusive learning environment has challenged me to think outside the box. I had plenty of opportunities to explore my academic and non-academic curiosities. It taught me lifelong skills that no textbooks could – there were a lot of fun and challenging hands-on projects, which allowed me to connect my studies to the real world. Whether academically or even just socially, I was able to transition from secondary school to university smoothly.</p>
