            <div class="lightbox" data-id="138">
            <div class="lightbox-wrapper">
                <button class="close"></button>
                <div class="lightbox-container">
                    <time>28/01/2026</time>
                    <div class="lightbox-content">
                                                    <h3>𝗔 𝗟𝗶𝘃𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗛𝗶𝘀𝘁𝗼𝗿𝘆 𝗟𝗲𝘀𝘀𝗼𝗻<br>27 January marked International Holocaust Remembrance Day, officially proclaimed by the United Nations General Assembly in 2005 to coincide with the 60th anniversary of the liberation of the Auschwitz-Birkenau concentration camp.<br>Yesterday, ESF South Island School hosted a profoundly moving session organised by the Hong Kong Holocaust and Tolerance Centre. Our students were honoured to hear from Madame Larissa Cain, a survivor of the Warsaw Ghetto, who shared her firsthand testimony.<br><br>#RCHK #HolocaustRemembranceDay #LivingHistory #Tolerance @esf_sis</h3>
