            <div class="lightbox" data-id="136">
            <div class="lightbox-wrapper">
                <button class="close"></button>
                <div class="lightbox-container">
                    <time>20/01/2026</time>
                    <div class="lightbox-content">
                                                    <h3>Choosing a future path is a critical journey, yet the right direction isn't always clear. This is where our RCHK Career Counsellors come in! Committed to providing secondary students with continuous guidance and the resources they need to make well-informed decisions, the Further Education (FE) team recently hosted a Mini University Fair for Years 10–13 students.<br><br>While smaller in scale than our large annual RCHK Fair, this event provided a focused environment featuring a select group of UK universities and Hong Kong-based representatives. Students had an opportunity to engage in one-on-one conversations and ask detailed questions about their prospective academic careers.<br><br>#rchk #opportunity #universityapplication #universityfair #education @esf_englishschoolsfoundation</h3>
